            <lg xml:id="TK91">
<l>iṉcolā līra maḷaiip paṭiṟilavāñ</l>
<l>cemporuḷ kaṇṭārvāyc col</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Sweet words indeed are the true words of those who've seen the real truth,</l>
<l>mingled with mercy, free of falsehood.</l>
            </lg>
